 first test of\nquantum non-locality for \"massive\" degrees of freedom (i.e., for degrees of\nfreedom describing the motion of massive particles).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Sep 2008 21:23:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-07-05"}
