oud at the systemic velocity of ~85 km/s enables us to place\nthe SNR at a kinematic distance of 5.2 kpc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Sep 2008 05:35:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Oct 2008 11:20:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 17 Jan 2009 16:38:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
