rocedures. They permit a secure type and\nredshift determination in about 80% of cases. The present paper illustrates\ntheir performances on a few sample spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Sep 2008 14:17:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
